Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:11.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上的羽翼　已经与你一同消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:19.68,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔时的记忆　却无法像擦伤一样消去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:35.99,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你寻回　是我一直所想之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:43.66,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你不随时间的浊流　被浪冲走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:51.46,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法说出些许回忆　始终无依无靠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:59.47,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残留下的些许眼泪　却一定无法传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:05.73,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的泪滴　也将坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:13.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间黑夜被撕裂　光芒飞散于空中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:21.58,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洁净如洗的太阳　温柔地照耀着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:26.21,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱着你一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:39.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After the rain　等到雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:46.53,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,across the rainbow　就飞越彩虹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:53.58,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在彩虹被蓝天遮掩前　告诉它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:23:02.00,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:10.59,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何会被忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:16.06,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝物的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:25.98,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After the rain　等到雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:33.24,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,across the rainbow　从哪里开始说起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:40.16,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤不会消失　所以悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:49.47,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些点缀在快乐的回忆里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的太古时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自亚芬诺亚山脉另一边的真王之祖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降临在塔海亚泽之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材魁梧 拥有金色眼瞳的王祖杰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人们见识到了真正圣洁的神的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和拉扎的战争开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要有所伤亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有英勇的大公军队和斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军必定胜利无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 鲁甘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快射 快射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军正因为拥有斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能守护真王的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到万人尊敬的真王统治的王土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由勇猛的大公军坚守
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维系着恒久不变的繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远离战场有一个很小的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村庄的名字叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚凯村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大公的领土上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是座用来饲养斗蛇的特别的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见艾琳了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:05:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个女人竟担任斗蛇的医术师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小艾琳啊 是不是在干活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是也差不多该收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚刚在药材屋的后面看到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看到了 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在药材屋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳好像又迷上什么怪玩意儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是做了一半…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 蚱蜢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么蚱蜢啊 该吃中饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是答应我上午都用弑羊草扎草球的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做斗蛇宝宝用的特效水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以来找材料了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特效水是要混合斗蛇身体的粘液
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝下来才能让身体变得强壮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去除寄生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 对刚刚出生的斗蛇宝宝来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成年斗蛇使用的特效水药性太烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要在斗蛇宝宝变强壮以前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用驱虫的草球来把斗蛇宝宝洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳觉得和母亲一起的日子很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为只有她们两人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才很珍惜彼此在一起生活的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 斗蛇宝宝长大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我想过些时候它应该可以吃普通饲料了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在把它放到池子里还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等能放到池子里去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去照顾宝宝行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要成为妈妈那样的斗蛇医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你再长大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还这么想的话 我就考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池子里不仅仅有斗蛇宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很可怕的成年斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇不是很乖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像根木头似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不怎么爱动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是设法让它们顺从而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用无形的枷锁束缚着它们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索永
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把斗蛇从战场搬回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈先过去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴 按住尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想办法镇住它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索永
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:08:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索永
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了 艾琳的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吹了一声哨子就让斗蛇服服帖帖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浇点水上去 让它尽快凉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让它的身体缺水 想办法多敷些湿的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让一让 让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是瓦单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备送去放养 没听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是斗蛇宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 快点让开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小家伙要运到池子里去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说还没到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈说还没到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色的眼瞳 雾之民的女儿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个雾之民女人 我照顾斗蛇的时间更长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是由我看过后决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看 可以运到池子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先让我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来差不多可以吃饲料了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在放入池子前 请先给它涂上斗蛇的体液
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 它的窝一定要用新草铺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 喂 咱们走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈今天可能要晚点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你吵醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:12:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻到麝香样的斗蛇味道 就知道是妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇宝宝还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 很精神的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够和妈妈一起睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 两个人一起会更暖和些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每逢早晨 男人们都去饲养斗蛇的池子干活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下的女人们和小孩子则开始做家务或到田里劳动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这天早晨的情形却与以往有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索永
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啦 那个斗蛇宝宝不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找不到的话 就要按村子里的规矩办了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦单先生 运送小家伙的不就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是这个女人允许我把它放养到池子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在当务之急是先找到那个小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有悔过之意 所以才说雾之民的人多么卑劣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈去一下池子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得找到斗蛇宝宝才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子里 有专门饲养斗蛇的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为斗蛇的岩屋的钟乳石洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钟乳石洞里 有多条叫做斗蛇道的水路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有专门储水的水池
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一个个水池就是用来饲养斗蛇的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就如同是这个村子的宝藏一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是必须要守护的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头领 那个斗蛇宝宝逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到池子外面去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 我想它还在这里的某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦单 你召集男人们去池子里找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索永啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:15:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我冒着触犯规条的危险让你留在村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你们雾之民的智慧和兽医术以及亚逊的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子不能进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是头领的孙女也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去找 快去找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷的跑进去会被骂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是村子里的头等大事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别嘀咕 跟着做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 等一等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好危险… 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是小心一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水从山上流向岩石洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇有可能顺着水流到这里的池子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把斗蛇宝宝池里的水抽干了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再看看别的池子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许跑到那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 什么时候才能让我们去照顾牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙可是大公大人赐予的宝贝斗蛇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有得到头领允许的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是索永不是在照顾了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是头领决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水被抽干了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是斗蛇宝宝的池子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是旧草
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧草会发酵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以变热
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 很烫手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还很难闻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈明明说过要用新草的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许还在这个池子里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它躲在这个里面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为讨厌旧草的味道 所以逃到这儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要松手了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 松手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从斗蛇宝宝池子那边传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索永
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昏睡过去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么跑到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到斗蛇宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了妈妈才来这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我偷偷跑进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次不要再做这样危险的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么逃掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为草没有换成新的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇宝宝讨厌那个味道和热度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才躲在洞里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦单
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没有弄脏 我以为不换不要紧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇是非常敏感的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是非常小的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请你务必按照我的指示去执行好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳 今天害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是想成为像妈妈那样的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:22:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村庄只能以饲养斗蛇为生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过斗蛇和我们人类终究还是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点你一定要记住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇是野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳还不能完全理解这句话的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 艾琳认识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.51,0:22:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗蛇并不是单纯老实听话的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:06.49,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚凯村里来一位大哥 他带来了自己生病的斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:08.06,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引来村子里一片喧闹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.28,0:24:12.64,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要找这里最好的医生来照看他的斗蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.89,0:24:15.30,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到这 就得轮我妈妈登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.36,0:24:18.36,toDefault2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了妈妈 我要加油努力
